## ðŸ”§ Implementation Guidelines

### **Code Standards:**
- **ES5 compatibility** for code.js (Figma plugin constraint)
- **Complete ui.html** files (no diffs for UI changes)
- **Maintain existing functionality** - no breaking changes
- **Professional logging** for all operations
- **TypeScript strict mode** compliance

### **Testing Requirements:**
- **Build verification** after each change
- **Manual testing** of implemented feature
- **Regression testing** of existing functionality
- **Edge case validation** (empty states, errors, large data)

### **Progress Tracking:**
- **Update thread memory** after each successful implementation
- **Document blockers** with specific solutions needed
- **Log time spent** on each seed
- **Note dependencies** between seeds

